T1  - Performance factors of small tourism ventures: The interface of tourism, entrepreneurship and the environment
AU  - Lerner, Miri
AU  - Haber, Sigal
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 16
IS  - 1
SP  - 77
EP  - 100
PY  - 2001
DA  - 2001/01/01/
